WEBVTT

00:07.498 --> 00:09.215
How do I get to the Red Cafe?

00:09.511 --> 00:10.376
The Red Cafe?

00:11.165 --> 00:11.841
Let's see.

00:13.491 --> 00:15.715
Go to the corner and turn left.

00:15.964 --> 00:16.367
Left.

00:16.832 --> 00:19.133
Go two blocks and turn right.

00:19.486 --> 00:20.015
Right.

00:20.643 --> 00:22.881
Around the corner is a train station.

00:23.397 --> 00:24.045
Take the train.

00:24.318 --> 00:25.375
Don't take the train.

00:26.091 --> 00:30.410
Go through the station across the street to the bookstore.

00:31.233 --> 00:33.937
Next to the bookstore is a pharmacy.

00:34.300 --> 00:36.944
Next to the pharmacy is the Red Cafe.

00:37.115 --> 00:37.537
Yes.

00:38.197 --> 00:38.535
Got it?

00:40.493 --> 00:41.433
Let's do it again.

00:43.027 --> 00:47.517
Corner left, two blocks, right.

00:48.263 --> 00:53.623
Around the corner, don't take the train, through the station, across the street.

00:53.978 --> 00:57.475
Bookstore, pharmacy, Red Cafe.

00:57.877 --> 00:58.792
Thank you very much.

00:58.892 --> 00:59.741
You're very welcome.

